-- Aston Villa Signs Striker Robbie Keane on Two-Month Loan From L.A. Galaxy
-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 2012-01-12T10:36:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/aston-villa-signs-striker-robbie-keane-on-two-month-loan-from-l-a-galaxy.html
Aston Villa  signed Ireland striker
Robbie Keane on a two-month loan from  Major League Soccer ’s Los
Angeles Galaxy, subject to international clearance from the
sport’s governing body FIFA.  The 31-year-old will be available for Villa’s Premier
League home match against Everton in two days, up to and
including its game at Wigan on Feb. 25, the club said on its
website.  “I’m delighted to be back in the Premier League,” Keane
 told Villa’s website . “I’m excited about it and I know I’ll
really enjoy my time here.”  Keane, who has played in the Premier League for most of his
career, joined the Galaxy from Tottenham in August.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 James Cone  at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  